{
  "stem": "25651.5",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Not only was it pretty, but it tasted good.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It almost tasted as good as chocolate.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And, of course, we were starved for sweet and sugar.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So once a week we had buchty [SPEAKING CZECH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That was a treat.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my brother, Milos, was making this buchty, and he said, you come to this and this window at the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a special kitchen where the cooking was done for children, because there were four or five of these buildings, huge things.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, big organization.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My own school, which is now, by the way, the Museum of Theresienstadt, the same building, L-417 in the-- in the counting of Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Each-- each house had a number according to the grid reference.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this kitchen was in L-318, which was one block away.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Near the other fence, actually.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This-- you know the road that went through which divided north and south Theresienstadt, or Terezin, in Czech.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he said, I'm going to be making these cakes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And every other one or so, I'll throw out of the window.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you'll stand outside the window and catch them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, I never realized this, but when somebody throws a tennis ball at you, to catch a tennis ball, you actually-- your reflex action follows the hand that's throwing, and you move whilst the hand is throwing.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's tremendously difficult-- I don't know if you have ever tried it, but if you want a bit of fun, try a bit of dough, like bread dough, you know, just a-- like a piece of cake, but it's just a piece of dough, and throw it out of your first floor window at your children, grownups, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 59
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Good sportsman or bad, they won't catch them.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
